{
  "stem": "1169.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It absolutely-- it was a dead subject [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the world, and even in our Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was, like, dormant-- totally dormant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It's possible we needed more time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I only know that that period is as vivid in front of my eyes as things that happened yesterday, if not more.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because it was so-- so traumatic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I'm pleased that finally the world is going to know it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because in Bergen-Belsen we really had two fears.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "One, that we'll never get out alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And two, that they will kill us and no one's going to know about it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That was even worse than getting killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that's the reason I think this is proper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It's only right as a religious Jew or just even as a plain Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I think this is a proper opportunity to thank God for his great mercies that he enabled us to live to this day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I think one should even recite a blessing of [NON-ENGLISH] at such an occasion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It's the first time in-- since the Holocaust that I'm actually relating this story to an official body.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Over there, we were sure we would not live.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And-- and no one would ever find out about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The Germans camouflaged everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I consider this a great moment in my life to be able to relate this story.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I think I should also express my [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] most deep-felt gratitude [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] to",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, for a moment, you know, I get so excited.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Steven Spielberg, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I consider him a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
